## 🔥 Firestore 쿼리 패턴

### 오늘 용병
```typescript
guest_players
where status == "open"
where date == today
orderBy time (asc)
limit 5
```

### 오늘 경기
```typescript
matches
where status == "open"
where date == today
orderBy time (asc)
limit 5
```

### 최신 모집
```typescript
recruits
where status == "open"
where createdAt >= 3일 전
orderBy createdAt (desc)
limit 5
```

### 지역 팀
```typescript
teams
where region == user.region
orderBy createdAt (desc)
limit 5
```

